- Create new project
- npm init -y
- install babel modules, webpack and react modules
- wrtite code for Index.html
- refer Bootstrap in index.html for Responsive design
- create main.js  (Entry point with default state) in client folder.
- Create components folder and start creating React components
- App.js contain main layout of Shopping app. Refer Login, Products and CartInfo.
- Write Login.js code 
- Write Product.js to  show all the products.
- Write ShoppingCart.js for updating shopping cart.
- Write SearchBar.js for searching products
- Write TextInput.js  for accepting search text
- Write TextDisplay.js 